{"tid":1048572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2009年落馬洲車禍六死，醉駕司機輕傷判監六年","createTime":"2019-03-05T18:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T15:44:20.000Z","uid":92750,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f1fe549fb5265a9fb5059f49be1686cdd4446119","tid":1048572,"uid":92750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"當日上午，5名紮鐵工人於落馬洲一起乘坐新界的士，前往懲教署轄下的羅湖懲教所建築地盤上班。7時10分，當的士駛至青山公路洲頭段時，一輛反方向行駛的16噸貨車疑因左搖右擺並越過對面行車線，與的士迎頭相撞，之後貨車並沒有減速，再剷上的士車頂，壓毀的士，然後推行的士約50米，的士撞及鐵欄剷上行人路掉頭停下；貨車則撞到大樹後向左翻側。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場後，須將的士車頂撬開，救出的士內的5名乘客及1名的士司機，之後隨即證實他們全部死亡，受輕傷的貨車司機則自行爬出車外，於接受酒精測試時驗出體內酒精含量超標，警方以危險駕駛導致他人死亡及醉酒駕駛的罪名，把他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n時任行政長官曾蔭權、運輸及房屋局局長鄭汝樺、職工盟立法會議員李卓人等到場視察及慰問死者家屬（因當中遇難者為職工盟紥鐵團結工會理事），有家屬激動下跪要求曾蔭權嚴懲醉酒司機，政府則考慮修例增加酒後駕駛的刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當日仲要係農曆年尾最後一日開工，做完就收爐。條廢中就醉駕撞撚死咗一車人。<br />\n<br />\n坐得嗰六年，出到嚟就勁啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ehcPH9nB-B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FehcPH9nB-B8&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXnjCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=6a35af53\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ehcPH9nB-B8</a><br />\n仲要帶埋大陸老婆囡落嚟香港<br />\n政府邀請佢拍條片叫人唔好醉駕又唔制，又驚人歧視佢坐咗監，6條人命死咗係你手呀仆街<br />\n<br />\n死廢中就番上大陸獻世啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953326713bc362f2e1563ded9eee872661c871a8","tid":1048572,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9431471f4c80b48986209c16ac11ac496528598","tid":1048572,"uid":117509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:10:58.000Z","msg":"個理事如果係公賊會應該會判多十碌"},{"pid":"ccd4ea15dd5193dd944a655b7d005480280ba971","tid":1048572,"uid":92750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:19:19.000Z","msg":"依啲廢中死十次都唔夠"},{"pid":"14ce4b56d01800b56620418db4c97f22971c211a","tid":1048572,"uid":81273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"製造六個單親家庭"},{"pid":"3ddb17d307375afdeb8a4b06c1547d1528aa81ea","tid":1048572,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T19:19:57.000Z","msg":"點解判咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed6fc027fd17ca994a2371cd7a9777e84f4ddfd","tid":1048572,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"一條命一年？"},{"pid":"46cacce8d5b4e0c71b18c6e5f95e160dc2419858","tid":1048572,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T19:27:57.000Z","msg":"梁天琦都係六年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e584cc63077fbaeebdf0abb9d0901b498184014","tid":1048572,"uid":155253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"6條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511e00bd53c14d2c537ccd643ad05192b6e20c95","tid":1048572,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死仆街 有無人起底"},{"pid":"9e4e854a8c5e615b5778d1e6d8dd79595fa2f756","tid":1048572,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"判咁少 一次過殺左咁多人既老豆<img src=\"/assets/face